## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped

**1. /runs show with step detail (GH#436 MVP item)**
- `/runs show <id>` — full run detail: workflow name, status, timestamps, tokens, all steps with position/provider/duration/output size
- `/runs show <id> step <n>` — view individual step output, provider, model, duration
- `/runs list` now shows short IDs for use with `/runs show`
- Short ID prefix matching — type first 4-8 chars of an ID
- Autocomplete for run IDs — `/runs show` tab shows recent runs with status and workflow name

**2. /settings consolidation**
- `/settings about` — version, engine path, working directory
- `/settings providers` — AI provider list
- `/settings connections` — all connections (providers + MCP + cloud services)
- `/settings config` — show config values
- `/settings set <key> <value>` — update config

